

This folder contains dataset files used in the project:

- Source: Kaggle - UCI HAR Dataset
- Features: 561 sensor-based features
- Classes: 6 activity labels
- Participants: 30 volunteers



Test csv : "https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/uciml/human-activity-recognition-with-smartphones?select=test.csv
Train csv : https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/uciml/human-activity-recognition-with-smartphones?select=train.csv
[Download Train CSV](https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/uciml/human-activity-recognition-with-smartphones?select=train.csv)
[Download Test CSV](https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/uciml/human-activity-recognition-with-smartphones?select=test.csv)
